cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the security and privacy challenges in the healthcare industry, specifically related to the use of BYOD, PANs, and IoT. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the role of healthcare professionals in securing patient data, which falls under the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The use of instant messaging and cloud technology is also mentioned, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper discusses the need for awareness and education, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
